OL,3,COpportunities for islanders to mark
OL,4,CHolocaust Memorial Day
OL,6,FThere are a number of ways islanders
OL,7,Fcan mark on Saturday 27 January.
OL,9,FIn at 1pm, wreaths will be laid at the
OL,10,Fmemorials in White Rock, North Beach,
OL,11,FSt Peter Port.
OL,13,FThere will also be a gathering at the
OL,14,FPrincess Royal Centre for Performing
OL,15,FArts from 5pm until 6pm which will
OL,16,Fcommemorate victims of the atrocity,
OL,17,Fas well as other acts of genocide.
