OL,3,COpportunities for islanders to mark
OL,4,CHolocaust Memorial Day
OL,6,FIt will be led by the Very Reverend
OL,7,FTim Barker, with Sabit Jakupovic MBE
OL,8,Fas the guest speaker, who will share
OL,9,Fhis story of being imprisoned for 120
OL,10,Fdays in two different concentration
OL,11,Fcamps.
OL,13,FDuring the event, Guernsey Music
OL,14,FService Year 6 pupil Solomon Bearder
OL,15,Fwill play the cello - there will also
OL,16,Fbe spoken word by members of the
OL,17,FGuernsey Institute's performing arts
OL,18,Fcourse.
