OL,6,FFor islanders in , a service will be
OL,7,Fheld at the Hammond Memorial with a
OL,8,Fprayer led by Bishop Michael Langridge
OL,9,Fon behalf of Alderney Churches
OL,10,FTogether.
OL,12,FA wreath will then be laid by the
