OL,3,COpportunities for islanders to mark
OL,4,CHolocaust Memorial Day
OL,6,FThe guest speaker is Smajo Beso,
OL,7,Ffounder of the Bosnian Genocide
OL,8,FEducation Trust, a charity which
OL,9,Fcommemorates the murder of at least
OL,10,F8,000 men and boys in the town of
OL,11,FSrebrenica in July 1995 during the
OL,12,FYugoslav wars.
OL,14,FSeveral relatives of his were tortured
OL,15,Fin concentration camps during the
OL,16,Fconflict, forcing him and his family
OL,17,Fto flee the country to go to the UK as
OL,18,Frefugees in the 1990s.
