OL,4,CHolocaust Memorial Day
OL,6,FAfter the talk, members of the Jersey
OL,7,FArts Centre Youth Theatre will deliver
OL,8,Freadings and the Dean of Jersey, The
OL,9,FVery Rev Mike Keirle, will give the
OL,10,Fclosing address.
OL,12,FThis will be followed by the laying of
OL,13,Fwreaths at the Lighthouse Memorial,
OL,14,Fand will be led by Dr Karen Kyd, wife
OL,15,Fof the Lieutenant Governor, on behalf
OL,16,Fof the Crown.
